-- Spain Power Price Must Rise 17% on Court Ruling, Cinco Dias Says
-- B y   B e n   S i l l s
-- 2012-03-15T06:29:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-15/spain-power-price-must-rise-17-on-court-ruling-cinco-dias-says.html
The Spanish government will have to
raise power prices by 17 percent to comply with a ruling by the
 Supreme Court , Cinco Dias reported, citing estimates from the
power companies.  The court this week said that the Industry Ministry must
increase prices to cover an additional 900 million euros ($1.2
billion) of costs, the newspaper said.  Click here for web link  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
